lvmcfg (1.14) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Frans Pop ]
  * Remove Thorsten Sauter from uploaders as requested by MIA team.
  * lvmcfg should not be used on architectures that use partman. As partman
    can also be present on architectures that do not use it, we check instead
    if partitioner is installed; only if it is, lvmcfg is listed in the menu.

